description:
With this application you can get tips and tricks for the prevention of joint pain, as well as upload a picture or photograph of your joint and find out the estimated degree of illness *.

Rheumatic diseases are quite common these days, and the number of people with joint pain is growing every year.

 Think about the consequences 
Throughout our lives, at least once, each of us has experienced joint pain - aching, dull, muffled, sharp, or even unbearable.
Pain in the joints bothers a person from time to time, regardless of age and activity. In addition, pain limits the movement of a person and often causes discomfort throughout the body.  Most ignore the first "signs" of a future serious illness  associated with joints. We want to assure you that there may be irreversible consequences if you do not think right now.  We recommend that you take care of your health and familiarize yourself with the application , which will share tips and advice with you.

 Customized Technique: 
The recommendations are for different symptoms and suspected joint diseases, and not common to everyone. In the application you can take a survey, the results of which you can get recommendations.
 Thanks to the recommendations , you can get more information about these diseases:
- rheumatism;
- rheumatoid arthritis;
- rheumatic polyarthritis;
- osteochondrosis;
- osteoarthrosis;
- osteoporosis;
- scoliosis;
- arthrosis;
- lumbosacral radiculitis;
- deforming spondylarthrosis.

 Start exploring joint pain today 
It will be enough to download the application and begin to study the topic of joint pain that can cause discomfort in your body.

 * Disclaimer:  The information provided is not a medical opinion, a doctor must be visited to make a diagnosis.

 Movement is life for your health
